HEADWORD: Monembryony
<hw>Mon*em"bry*o*ny</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Mono-</er>, and <er>Embryo</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>The
condition of an ovule having but a single embryo.</def> --
